  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA41">
<l>valiyam eṉaniṉaintu vantetirnta mallar</l>
<l>valiya muṭiyiṭiya vāṅki, valiyaniṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉāḻik kaiyāl puṭaittiṭuti kīḷātē,</l>
<l>paṉṉāḷum niṟkumip pār.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bending, so that they crumbled, the strong heads</l>
<l>of the wrestlers who faced [you], having come thinking “we are strong”</l>
<l>you would thrash them with your strong golden-discus hand. Without being torn</l>
<l>this earth will stand for many days.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
